snippet.title: SM64 Jammin' Journey - Course 1 Peaceful Paradise
snippet.description:
Welcome to my walkthrough of SM64 Jammin' Journey a Super Mario 64 modification by goosedajuice. In this video, I show off how to get all 7 stars in Course 1 Peaceful Paradise as well as 1 of the Overworld Stars, which are at these times:

Red Coins of the Overworld  2:06

Course 1 Peaceful Paradise

Dark Side of the 'Shroom  3:41
Opening the Cannon + Pillar Skippin'  4:57
Underwater Crevice  6:23
Chompin' Clam Secrets  6:52
Red Coins in the Stony Seabed + 100 Coins  9:00
The Ship's Loot  11:57

Comments: I'm back. (I was only gone a week. Please calm the flip down.) Anyways, this hack was pretty neat.

Mario Screen Music: ???
File Select Music: Paper Mario - File Select Screen
Tutorial Area Music: Zelda Ocarina of Time - Kakariko Village
Toad Music: A Hat in Time - ???
Overworld Music: ???
Star Select Music: Super Mario RPG - Nimbus Land
Course 1 (Main) Music: Mario Party - Yoshi's Tropical Island
Course 1 (Dark Shrooms) Music: ???
Course 1 (Pirate Ship) Music: ???

DL: https://sites.google.com/view/supermario64romhacks/patch-downloads
